                          "code": "\tdef getTags(path, tags):\n\t\trequiresAttention \u003d False\n\t\tisComplete \u003d False\n\t\tret \u003d []\n\t\t\n\t\tfor tag in tags:\n\t\t\tsubPath \u003d tag[\"name\"] if path \u003d\u003d \"\" else \"%s/%s\" % (path, tag[\"name\"])\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\tif tag[\"tagType\"] \u003d\u003d \"Folder\":\n\t\t\t\t(requiresAttentionTmp, isCompleteTmp, items) \u003d getTags(subPath, [] if \"tags\" not in tag else tag[\"tags\"])\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tif requiresAttentionTmp:\n\t\t\t\t\trequiresAttention \u003d True\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tif isCompleteTmp:\n\t\t\t\t\tisComplete \u003d True\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tret.append({\n\t\t\t\t\t\"label\": tag[\"name\"],\n\t\t\t\t    \"expanded\": True,\n\t\t\t\t    \"data\": {\n\t\t\t\t    \t\"path\": subPath\n\t\t\t\t    },\n\t\t\t\t    \"items\": items,\n\t\t\t\t    \"icon\": {\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"path\": \"material/folder\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"color\": \"#D90000\" if requiresAttentionTmp else (\"#00AC00\" if isCompleteTmp else None),\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"style\": {}\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t})\n\t\t\telif tag[\"tagType\"] in (\"UdtType\", \"UdtInstance\"):\n\t\t\t\t(requiresAttentionTmp, isCompleteTmp, items) \u003d getTags(subPath, [] if \"tags\" not in tag else tag[\"tags\"])\n\t\t\t\trequiresAttentionTmp \u003d requiresAttentionTmp or (\"list\" in tag and not tag[\"list\"][\"complete\"])\n\t\t\t\tisCompleteTmp \u003d isCompleteTmp or (\"list\" in tag and tag[\"list\"][\"complete\"])\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tif requiresAttentionTmp:\n\t\t\t\t\trequiresAttention \u003d True\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tif isCompleteTmp:\n\t\t\t\t\tisComplete \u003d True\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\tret.append({\n\t\t\t\t\t\"label\": tag[\"name\"] if tag[\"typeId\"] \u003d\u003d \"\" else \"%s (%s)\" % (tag[\"name\"], tag[\"typeId\"]),\n\t\t\t\t    \"expanded\": requiresAttention,\n\t\t\t\t    \"data\": {\n\t\t\t\t    \t\"path\": subPath\n\t\t\t\t    },\n\t\t\t\t    \"items\": items,\n\t\t\t\t    \"icon\": {\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"path\": \"material/label\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"color\": \"#D90000\" if requiresAttentionTmp else (\"#00AC00\" if isCompleteTmp else None),\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"style\": {}\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t})\n\t\t\telif tag[\"tagType\"] \u003d\u003d \"AtomicTag\":\n\t\t\t\ttypeId \u003d tag[\"typeId\"] if \"typeId\" in tag and tag[\"typeId\"] !\u003d \"\" else \"\"\n\t\t\t\tret.append({\n\t\t\t\t\t\"label\": tag[\"name\"] if typeId \u003d\u003d \"\" else \"%s (%s)\" % (tag[\"name\"], typeId),\n\t\t\t\t    \"expanded\": False,\n\t\t\t\t    \"data\": {\n\t\t\t\t    \t\"path\": subPath\n\t\t\t\t    },\n\t\t\t\t    \"items\": [],\n\t\t\t\t    \"icon\": {\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"path\": \"material/label\",\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"color\": None,\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\"style\": {}\n\t\t\t\t\t}\n\t\t\t\t})\n\t\t\n\t\treturn (requiresAttention, isComplete, ret)\n\t\n\treturn [] if \"tags\" not in value else getTags(\"\", value[\"tags\"])[2]",
                          "type": "script"
